New modules can be added by pressing Insert. Modules can be moved up or down by pressing Ctrl + Cursor Up / Cursor Down. CRCs can be added to a module by pressing Shift+Insert when that module is selected, or just Insert if one of the existing CRCs if tha
\hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 t module is selected. A selected module or CRC can be deleted by pressi\hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 ng Delete.
\par \hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 If one or more CRCs has been added to a module, then the CRC of the currently loaded module must match one of these CRCs, otherwise the module is treated as if it wasn\hich\f46 \rquote \loch\f46 t present.
\par \hich\af46\dbch\af31505\loch\f46 Each module has a number of flags:
